The paper focuses on normalization methods for neural networks, which is a common topic in machine learning and deep learning research. The paper specifically addresses the issue of elimination singularities, which are related to the optimization of neural networks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the paper evaluates the proposed method on image-related tasks. Other possible sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) since the paper deals with neural networks and their optimization.
